page.title: 16TRISCOMBE NURSERY
page.content:
At TRISCOMBE there is a nursery and garden centre. At the nursery they have vegetables, plants,fruit,and flowers. The vegetables they have are potatoes,carrots,cabages,sprouts,and onions.
The plants they have are spider plants,cactus plants,umbrella plants, and dragon plants plus lots more. The fruit they have are {RASPBERRIES, {STRAWBERRIES BLACKCURRANTS APPLES and {PEARS.} The flowers thy have are pansies and roses.The pansies come in blue, red, purple and white.The roses they have are blood,common,yellow,and dog roses.
